<collectingCountry id="B8CD762E9B7EFFF869702CEC56E8C054" box="[340,410,1771,1797]" name="China" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">China</collectingCountry>
Sea is sometimes called the West Philippine Sea), East 
<collectingCountry id="B8CD762E9B7EFFF86C0B2CEC5307C054" box="[1071,1141,1771,1797]" name="China" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">China</collectingCountry>
Sea, Bohol Sea, Gulf of Tomini, Bismarck Sea, Coral Sea, 
<collectingCountry id="B8CD762E9B7EFFF86A542D0955AEC079" box="[624,732,1806,1832]" name="Australia" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">Australia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="B8CD762E9B7EFFF86B312D0854C0C079" box="[789,946,1806,1833]" name="New Zealand" pageId="67" pageNumber="68">New Zealand</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="A44B4B4F9B7EFFF86BE62D08533EC078" author="OBIS" box="[962,1100,1807,1833]" pageId="67" pageNumber="68" refId="ref39746" refString="OBIS 2021. Ocean Biodiversity Information System. Available from www. obis. org [accessed 15 Aug. 2021]." type="book" year="2021">OBIS 2021</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
